[gd_scene load_steps=18 format=3]

; Dev-only greybox for the task-05 manual playtest (F6). Not wired into GameManager —
; mission flow is task 11. A GuardAI patrols the three waypoints (looping) with a child
; DetectionSensor + debug cone. Walk into its cone to get investigated/searched; sprint nearby
; to pull it off-route to the noise; it recovers and resumes when it finds nothing. A loose
; Body sits off the route — step out of the way and let the guard's cone sweep over it to watch
; the alarm trip. Movement is direct steering on the open floor (no nav-mesh bake needed).

